--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-11-29)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (rest_server_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.3.3 (2020-11-22)
B: Add missing 'gnu_tar' dependency

* Version 0.3.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify checksum verification

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-10-26)
F: Update 'rest-server' to version '0.10.0'
C: Set '--no-auth' by default (to activate, create: /data/rest-server/.htpasswd)

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-10-19)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-07-21)
F: Initial release
